@node "Adopt_Tagline" "Adopt Tagline"

 - Adopt Tagline -

This  adds the tagline of the current message (if there is one) to your own
"Tagline File"

Keyboard equivalence:  Right Amiga A
@endnode

@node "Adopt_Tag_to_File" "Adopt Tag to File"

 - Adopt Tag to File -

When you select this menu item, a filerequester will pop up allowing you to
select a file to add tha tagline of the current message to.

