@node "History" "History"

 - Program History -

XAmyBW is a program i am still making and making and making....

If you are a xenolink sysop and you want to become a registeerd beta tester
please contact @{"Āme " link "my" 0}.

0.0 t/m 0.25 The Starting fase

0.26 16-02-97

   Speedup the areamsg scanning by using TraverseMsgbase

   Change the options menu added usenetgating and added REPLYADDR kludge
   parsing.

   Removed the SCAN button, because we don't use it at this moment.
   To scan a bluewave packet can be relative fast but to scan a complete
   msgbase can take a little more time.

0.27 23-02-97

   Change the pointers Max files (1 foreach msgarea) for one big AreaInfo
   file, removed a bug in the reply/forward/crosspost handling.

   NO Scanning buildin, with this you can leave the scanning of a area for
   the time that you enter a msgarea and not at the starting of the program.
   
   This means a speedup when starting but the personal message count for
   a area isn't up to date.
   Please notice the list with personal mail (from the .waitingmail files)
   will always be checked, to see if al mail still exists.

   Now it is also possible to remove the .waitingmail file after XAmyBW
   has imported it.

   You can change the scanningsettings and the .waitingmail scannings in
   the options setting windows.
   
0.28 NOT RELEASED

   Made the displaying of the areas a bit faster by removing some string to
   number convertions.

0.29 NOT RELEASED

0.30 01-03-96

   First public release

Known bugs:

   Crosspost and carboncopy don't work when you use them from the pulldown
   menu, from the header it works fine.                  

   Sometimes when you quit the editor XAmyBW hangs with a busy pointer.....
  

@endnode

